name: Shockingbite
description:
Today I made a work summary of the art of photography in a digital frame.

It should be part of my plan to show it off in an open space somewhere in my city. No one knows that the plague that attacks the planet earth to this day has not ended.

These are some of my works in food photography. according to the title, "Shockingbite" to invite you to feel it before you actually touch it.
